824.
HEINRICH EDWARD ADOLPH WOLTERS (30),
PLEADED GUILTY to
uttering a transfer of 100 shares in the
New Balkis Eestering Company, Limited, knowing it to be forged;
also to uttering two transfers of 300 shares and 150 shares respectively in the
Transvaal Exploring Land' and Minerals Company, Limited, knowing it to be forged;
also to uttering an authority for the delivery of a transfer of shares, knowing it to be forged;
also to uttering a warrant for the payment of money, knowing it to be forged.
Twelve months' hard labour. —And
